GunGame Hide-And-Seek by Kirill Mysnik aka iPlayer, 2010

Counter-Terrorists VS Terrorists
Kill them all!

No buyplaces, no weapons. Only GunGame.


Map was optimised.

PS. This archive contains *.nav file , so you can play with bots without any "Sampling walkable space" etc. ICQ: 3-189-212
